Product Description

Champion Heritage Collection - Boys Slim Fit Brushed Fleece Sweatpants

Champion Heritage Collection Boys Slim Fit Jogger Pant

A Heritage Collection favorite with a slightly slimmer modern cut. This sweatpant is a brushed fleece which gives the jogger a super soft hand feel that is comfortable and will keep you warm. Features two slanted side pockets. The pant is complete with Champion's signature embroidered logo or script logo detail.

  • BRUSHED FLEECE SWEATPANT: This boys jogger is a super soft brushed fleece fabric that keeps you warm and comfortable during the cold winter months. These will run small. We recommend ordering a size up.
  • CHAMPION HERITAGE COLLECTION: Celebrating Champion's Brand DNA, Champion heritage fleece joggers offers Champion's classic looks with a modern update. Grab other items from our heritage collection for easy classic Champion color matches.
  • DUAL SIDE POCKETS: Sweatpant comes with two side pockets for the essentials.
  • USES: Perfect sweatpants for any athletic activity including, basketball, football, soccer, dance, gym class or to just casually wear at home as a comfortable warm pant. Match this back to our sweatshirts or tee shirts to complete the outfit!
  • FLEECE LINED SWEATPANT: The sweatpant features Soft-twist fleece lining, a quality brushed fleece which is super comfortable and warm. The perfect comfortable sweatpant with our signature logos. While built for active boys, we love seeing success stories in our reviews from shorter petite women looking for sweatpants that fit. We’re happy when anyone enjoys the Champion classics.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

I wasn’t sure what size to buy since the reviews were all over the place and mostly for boys. I’m 5 feet tall and weigh 104lbs. The large was perfect for me! Will definitely get these in another color!!
